title: My Dearest
author: Bluetape
pages:
#- 

§0A tear drop, your laugh and a smile, your voice your eyes all in a pile.§r

§0Until heavenly hands from above created not just a rose or a thousand stars§r
#- but a reflection of perfection, beauty in its rarest form

§0those heavenly hands from above created you the one I love to love.§r

